gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nets 106, Raptors 102
gameRecap.excerpt: Brooklyn defeats Toronto, 106-102. For Brooklyn, Cam Thomas led the way with 23 points (five 3PM) and four rebounds while aided by Dennis Schroder (21 points, seven rebounds, nine assists) and Nic Claxton (14 points, 11 rebounds, five blocks) in the victory. Immanuel Quickley finished with a season-high 32 points, seven rebounds, and nine assists with Gradey Dick adding 24 points (career-high six 3PM) and four rebounds for Toronto in the losing effort. Brooklyn improves to 32-48, while Toronto moves to 25-55 in the loss.
